                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/100531948/">向往阳光</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-01-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">从贞观之治到开元盛世，到安史之乱。。。王朝兴衰史总让人心中奏起一轮悲歌，感慨于贤明帝王们的宏图大志和励精图治，也同情于末代帝王们的任人宰割和山河破碎。看完这部书，去广图搜索了很多自己感兴趣的唐代历史人物逸事的书籍，最深刻的便是李隆基这一生的跌宕起伏，一个人的转变是如此之快，却也说明理性的旗帜要想长久地战胜人性之弱点，那是天方夜谭啊</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1043692745">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1043692745" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1043692745" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1043692745">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2674938/">吟游诗人</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-05-21</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">历史爱好者当然是必读，欧阳修宋祁修书的详尽度和深度比旧唐书要好不少，表志可以使读者更好理解史实，关于其他种族部落的记载也较为丰富</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1040171540">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1040171540" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1040171540" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1040171540">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/137833366/">dust</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-05-10</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">浸染着的都是欧阳修的风骨，红杏尚书纂亦值得一读</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

